    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此乃霸道！！成为征服世界的魔王吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烧毁村落的女性向♀＞♂魔王军养成SLG《MURAYAKI VILLAIN》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/ebc8a31424faded18e29821a4902213f.avif?t=1736313016\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为比任何人都强大的魔王，站在最前线，将这个世界掌握在自己手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款♀&gt;♂真格反派游戏♡　适合不想成为被保护的公主，而想成为搞破坏的黑暗英雄的淑女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/8f0b7053759e4548e7e3becee8152cd6.webp?t=1736313016\" width=300 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/0e140e176dad07603b24ddeea78ad598.poster.avif?t=1736313016\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/0e140e176dad07603b24ddeea78ad598.webm?t=1736313016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/0e140e176dad07603b24ddeea78ad598.mp4?t=1736313016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目的是透过烧毁人类村落来扩张魔物的领土，并征服世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔王城和武器全都被人类夺走的主角使用的武器是……「平底锅」！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领助手，时而折磨助手引出负面力量，为地狱之火添加柴火！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/f6dcdf3803f707c6d4615a1e7d3e434a.webp?t=1736313016\" width=300 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/edb8aa7fa1fc70633e834baf0514d31e.avif?t=1736313016\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras_big/edb8aa7fa1fc70633e834baf0514d31e.avif?t=1736313016 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角是魔王成千的后裔中唯一的幸存者。当然，魔王军也被勇者歼灭了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有四只魔物因遭调职，未参与战斗而幸存，就指挥这四只「废柴」魔物工作，壮大魔王军吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/9214d0e20dda64891a2b8f26db526bc9.webp?t=1736313016\" width=300 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/0537d8a094e50cc705397f3bd7aedffc.avif?t=1736313016\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过做坏事可累积的「业力(Karma)」是魔王的魔力来源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要拥有业力，就能够为所欲为……！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/575fbfb0185624dc85cbca34c27b460b.webp?t=1736313016\" width=300 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras/6be54771df1f30e93083a147a0022e2f.avif?t=1736313016\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240910/extras_big/6be54771df1f30e93083a147a0022e2f.avif?t=1736313016 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为魔王，与部下互动也是重要的工作之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与他们去喝一杯或是聊聊天，提高忠诚度吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以将忠诚度高的魔物纳为「侧室」哦。目标将全员纳为侧室吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♀＞♂令人安心的五不保证！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧绝不逆转（自始至终不会轮到男角主导！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧女主角绝不脸红害羞（男角们非常会害羞！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧男角绝不说「我爱你」（不甜言蜜语、不疗妹！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧男角绝不说「我会保护你」（女主角才是最强的！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‧不与人类和解（要把人类的村落烧光！！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女攻男受魔王军养成SLG，献给想当邪恶又强大的女主角的玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就把本游戏放进您的愿望清单，踏出征服世界的第一步吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
